examgrader.model

Class Student

  • java.lang.Object
    • examgrader.model.Person
      • examgrader.model.Student
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Student>

    public class Student
extends Person
implements java.lang.Comparable<Student>, java.io.Serializable
    Represents a student and extends the abstract class Person. Each student has a first name, last name, student ID, and a list of StudentExams for every exam they have taken.
